      <title>南非大选后纷争让投资者陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非大选未能产生绝对胜利者，联盟谈判的结果仍存在很大不确定性，投资者准备迎接南非金融市场的进一步动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查预测莫迪获胜，印度股市创下新高，卢比上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/india-s-stock-futures-rally-as-polls-predict-landslide-modi-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在出口民意调查显示总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党取得压倒性胜利后，印度股市飙升至历史最高水平，而卢比和主权债券价格也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/india-s-stock-futures-rally-as-polls-predict-landslide-modi-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：降息预期坚定，亚洲股市早盘上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-as-rate-cut-bets-firm-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象显示亚洲制造业正在好转，美联储降息预期重燃，股市因此上涨。OPEC+ 制定恢复部分产量的计划后，油价出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-as-rate-cut-bets-firm-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 延长减产协议 但制定恢复石油供应计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/opec-has-outline-deal-extending-key-oil-production-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+ 延长了减产协议，以期提振脆弱的市场，同时也确定了在今年晚些时候恢复部分石油供应的日期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/opec-has-outline-deal-extending-key-oil-production-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 09:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
